I tried including the below imports,

```css
@import '../node_modules/bulma/sass/utilities/mixins.sass';
@import '../node_modules/bulma/sass/components/menu.sass';
```

And I ended up with new error.

```cmd
[23:21:34] Starting 'css:dev'...
